  "texts": [
    "Participants are briefed that the selected slider value is instantaneously applied to the chatbot, and they can dynamically adjust it throughout the conversation.",
    "CALIBRATE:Prior to entering the chatbot interface (Figure 7e), users perform a calibration step to initialize the steering strength that is applied to the conversation (Figure 7d).",
    "During calibration, pairwise outputs (Response A and B) for pre-written calibration questions are generated by sampling two different steering strengths, which initially set with disparate values of 𝑑 𝐴 = -100 and 𝑑 𝐵 = 100.",
    "Based on the user's preferred response, the steering strengths are updated to be closer to the preferred steering strength.",
    "For example, updating 𝑑 𝐴 ← (𝑑 𝐴 + 𝑑 𝐵)/2 to be closer to 𝑑 𝐵 if the preference is Slightly B."
  ],
